yond the term's own stanza\n+- direct annotations: `runoak -i amigo: associations GO:0140057` returned one PomBase annotation\n+- no in-repo evidence of mappings, subset membership, or taxon-constraint references for this term\n+\n+Validation:\n+- pre-validation: `make travis_build` passed before edits\n+- post-edit validation: `make travis_build` passed after obsoletion\n+\n+Checklist:\n+- [x] PLAN: analyzed issue context and intent\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: ontology validated before edits\n+- [N/A] RESEARCH: no literature research needed beyond preserving existing provenance\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: searched `go-edit.obo` for the term and all uses\n+- [N/A] DESIGN-PATTERNS: no new logical pattern work; simple obsoletion\n+- [x] EDITS: used `obo-checkout.pl` / `obo-checkin.pl` workflow with `terms/GO_0140057.obo`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: removed active axioms from obsolete term\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: used obsoletion workflow\n+- [x] METADATA: retained namespace and provenance; added term tracker item\n+- [x] AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: `make travis_build` passed after changes\n+- [x] REFERENCE-VALIDATION: preserved existing validated PMID reference\n+- [x] CHANGES-COMMITTED: committed only `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@\n+Obsoleted `GO:0140057` (`vacuole-mitochondria membrane tethering`) as requested.\n+\n+Summary:\n+- converted the term to an obsolete stanza\n+- retained the historical definition provenance\n+- added the issue tracker link to `#31876`\n+- removed the active asserted parent per GO obsoletion practice\n+\n+Checks performed:\n+- searched for ontology-internal refere